WEBVTT

00:00:00.913 --> 00:00:05.063
I'm going to start by saying something
you think you know to be true.

00:00:06.706 --> 00:00:09.992
Your brain creates
all facets of your mind.

00:00:11.133 --> 00:00:14.784
So then why do we treat
mental and physical illnesses

00:00:14.808 --> 00:00:15.982
so differently,

00:00:16.006 --> 00:00:18.737
if we think we know
that the mind comes from the brain?

00:00:20.197 --> 00:00:22.078
As a neuroscientist, I'm often told

00:00:22.102 --> 00:00:25.090
that I'm not allowed to study
how internal states

00:00:25.114 --> 00:00:28.592
like anxiety or craving or loneliness

00:00:28.616 --> 00:00:30.409
are represented by the brain,